"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8660419-relaxed-chalmers-in-top-shape-at-olympic-swim-trials\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A relaxed Kyle Chalmers says he's never been fitter and insists the pressure is off while chasing a slice of Olympic history.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyle Chalmers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  Chalmers is aiming to become the first Australian man to win two Olympic 100m freestyle gold medals.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9994445635868765, \"rank\": 0.0005433215083057165, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won gold in the event at the 2016 Rio Olympics and took silver at the Tokyo Games of 2021 when pipped by six-hundredths of a second by American Caleb Dressel.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5943348316848504, \"rank\": 0.6825522421300467, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"score\": 0.9999999014817198, \"rank\": 9.583401075496677e-08, \"text\": \"Caleb\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 25-year-old says if victory eludes him at the Paris Games starting next month, so be it.\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As you get older, I guess the pressure is off a little bit,\\\" Chalmers said after his initial swim at Australia's Olympic selection trials in Brisbane on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9988242294454703, \"rank\": 0.0007588879704901547, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9997429817105639, \"rank\": 0.00025696729433381826, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have kind of achieved everything I have set my mind to achieve in swimming so now I can just enjoy it and everything is a bonus.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As you get older you do not have as many competitions to look forward to so I am just slowing down and enjoying every little part of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chalmers advanced into Wednesday night's 50m freestyle final after a heat swim he used as a \\\"blowout\\\" ahead of his 100m freestyle races on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am absolutely in the best shape I have ever been and just super relaxed,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not feel like an Olympic trials and everything is on the line ... it's nice.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am staying with my girlfriend, my mum, my grandparents at an Airbnb.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Airbnb\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So just being able to escape back to them is keeping me very calm and relaxed.\\\"\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Associated Press  Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also includes evening update.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens  Do not miss updates on news about the Public Service.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\":